               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>Acts of Zä-Mikaˀel ˀArägawi and Gäbrä Krǝstos</p>
                     <p>I) ገድለ፡ዘሚካኤልአረጋዊ“Acts of Zä-Mikaˀel ˀArägawi” (fols. <locus from="1ra" to="44vb"/>) </p>
                     <p>II) ገድለ፡ገብረ፡ክርስቶስ“Acts of Gäbrä Krǝstos (St. Alexius)” (fols. <locus from="45ra" to="73vb"/>)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
